These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, italian, japanese, thai, turkish
There 7 different types of food: watermelon, avocado, lemon, artichoke, carrot, plum, kiwi
 1. the australian is between the italian and the turkish##2
 2. the french is in the middle##1
 3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 4. the japanese is between the person eating lemon and the person eating carrot##2
 5. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating lemon##2
 8. the person eating avocado is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the japanese is on the left of the thai##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
11. the thai is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | italian | australian | turkish | french    | indonesian | japanese   | thai    |
| Food         | plum  | avocado   | artichoke | watermelon | lemon   | kiwi | carrot |

