.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, classical, gospel, jazz, blues, punk
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the fan of classical is between the fan of blues and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the italian##1
5. the fan of electronic is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the fan of gospel is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Music-Genre          | jazz | classical | blues | electronic | punk | dubstep      | gospel  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

