.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german, indian, mexican, pakistani, polish
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, water, 7up, juice, mirinda, cola
 1. the mexican is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 3. the person drinking juice is the polish##1
 4. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the indian is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 8. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking cola and the indian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
10. the dutch is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | canadian | dutch   | indian | german | pakistani |
| Beverage           | juice | mirinda     | milk     | water | 7up   | tea   | cola    |

