.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, sprite, tea, water
The people have 7 different jobs:  designer, photographer, coach, social-worker, chef, entrepreneur, police-officer
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the coach##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the chef##1
 3. the entrepreneur is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the chef##1
 5. the designer is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the social-worker is between the person drinking juice and the entrepreneur##2
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the social-worker is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the photographer##1
10. the designer is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice    | sprite  | lemonade  | fanta  | water      | tea       | iced-tea |
| Job   | chef | social-worker | entrepreneur | police-officer | designer | coach | photographer  |

