.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, disco, folk, house, metal, punk, rock
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk, tea, 7up, fanta
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is the fan of disco##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of house##1
9. the fan of metal is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | metal | classical | folk | rock      | disco      | punk |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate | 7up | fanta       | almond-milk | iced-tea | tea | soy-milk |

