1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Hobby   | baking | video-games     | rock-climbing | magic-tricks | traveling | dancing  | skydiving |
