.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
7 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, frog, pony, chinchilla, turtle, snake
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, folk, house, pop, punk, reggae, salsa
 1. the owner of the ferret is the fan of salsa##1
 2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the pony and the fan of disco##2
 4. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of house##1
 6. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
 8. the owner of the frog is the fan of punk##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
10. the fan of pop is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Pet   | pony | ferret | goat  | chinchilla   | turtle | snake | frog |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | salsa       | disco | house | reggae  | folk   | punk   |

